function reset() {
    this.get("firstStringText").setTextString("Bein")
    this.get("secondStringText").setTextString("Zweige")
    
    this.get("Jaccard - Pane").reset()
    this.get("Levenshtein - Pane").reset()
    this.get("Damerau - Pane").reset()
    
    this.get("Jaccard - Pane").setVisible(false)
    this.get("Levenshtein - Pane").setVisible(false)
    this.get("Damerau - Pane").setVisible(false)
    this.get("LevenshteinLabel").setTextString("Levenshtein:")
    this.get("JaccardLabel").setTextString("Jaccard:")
    this.get("DamerauLabel").setTextString("Damerau-Levenshtein:")
    this.get("DiceLabel").setTextString("Dice:")
    this.activatedPane = ""
    
}

1554.source:
function showLevenshtein() {
    this.get("Levenshtein - Pane").setVisible(true)
    this.get("Jaccard - Pane").setVisible(false)
    this.get("Damerau - Pane").setVisible(false)
    
    this.activatedPane = "Levenshtein"
    var redColor = {color: Color.red}
    this.get("LevenshteinLabel").setTextString("")
    this.get("LevenshteinLabel").appendRichText("Levenshtein:", redColor)
    this.get("JaccardLabel").setTextString("Jaccard:")
    this.get("DamerauLabel").setTextString("Damerau-Levenshtein:")
    this.get("DiceLabel").setTextString("Dice:")
}

1558.source:
function showJaccard() {
    this.get("Jaccard - Pane").setVisible(true)
    this.get("Levenshtein - Pane").setVisible(false)
    this.get("Damerau - Pane").setVisible(false)
    
    this.activatedPane = "Jaccard"
    var redColor = {color: Color.red}
    this.get("JaccardLabel").setTextString("")
    this.get("JaccardLabel").appendRichText("Jaccard:", redColor)
    this.get("DiceLabel").setTextString("")
    this.get("DiceLabel").appendRichText("Dice:", redColor)
    this.get("LevenshteinLabel").setTextString("Levenshtein:")
    this.get("DamerauLabel").setTextString("Damerau-Levenshtein:")
}

1562.source:
function showDamerau() {
    this.get("Levenshtein - Pane").setVisible(false)
    this.get("Jaccard - Pane").setVisible(false)
    this.get("Damerau - Pane").setVisible(true)
    
    this.activatedPane = "Damerau"
    var redColor = {color: Color.red}
    this.get("DamerauLabel").setTextString("")
    this.get("DamerauLabel").appendRichText("Damerau-Levenshtein:", redColor)
    this.get("JaccardLabel").setTextString("Jaccard:")
    this.get("LevenshteinLabel").setTextString("Levenshtein:")
    this.get("DiceLabel").setTextString("Dice:")
}
